title: Netflix (NFLX) Casts Gabriel Leone as Lead of Senna Miniseries
description: Netflix (NFLX) is casting Gabriel Leone as its lead actor for the upcoming miniseries Senna, which will portray the life of the three-time F1 champion Aryton Senna da Silva.

title: Alig mozdulnak az amerikai tőzsdék
description: Minimális elmozdulások látszanak az amerikai tőzsdéken a nyitás után, a Dow Jones stagnál, a S&P 500 stagnál, míg a Nasdaq 0,3 százalékos pluszban áll.

title: Apple and Microsoft Weight in S&P 500 Reaches Record High
description: The combined weight of Apple and Microsoft, the largest two constituents, in the S&P 500, has reached an all-time high.
